    {
      "name": "Import CSV",
      "description": "Import pre-existing CSV data into a table.\n\nWorkflow:\n1. POST /data/import/preview — upload CSV, get column mapping + 10-row preview\n2. Review the suggested column mapping in the UI\n3. POST /data/import/commit — send the parsed rows with mode: append or replace\n\nmode values:\n  append  → INSERT rows into existing data (errors on PK conflict)\n  replace → TRUNCATE table first, then INSERT (safe re-run)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Import Preview (upload CSV)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": [],
                  "description": "Select your CSV file here"
                },
                {
                  "key": "connection_name",
                  "value": "{{connection_name}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "table",
                  "value": "tstg_aa_accountdetail",
                  "type": "text",
                  "description": "Target table name in the DB"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/data/import/preview",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "data", "import", "preview"]
            },
            "description": "Upload a CSV file and get:\n- First 10 rows as preview\n- Column names detected in the CSV\n- Column names in the target DB table\n- Auto-suggested CSV→DB column mapping (case-insensitive match)\n\nExpected response:\n```json\n{\n  \"file_name\": \"my_data.csv\",\n  \"csv_columns\": [\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", \"CURRENCY\"],\n  \"db_columns\": [\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", \"START_DATE\", \"CURRENCY\", ...],\n  \"suggested_mapping\": {\n    \"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"ARRANGEMENT_ID\",\n    \"VALUE_DATE\": \"VALUE_DATE\",\n    \"CURRENCY\": \"CURRENCY\"\n  },\n  \"preview_rows\": [{\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"AA001\", \"VALUE_DATE\": \"2024-01-01\", ...}],\n  \"connection\": \"DatagenDB\",\n  \"table\": \"tstg_aa_accountdetail\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Import Commit — Append",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"connection_name\": \"{{connection_name}}\",\n  \"table\": \"tstg_aa_accountdetail\",\n  \"mode\": \"append\",\n  \"columns\": [\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", \"START_DATE\", \"CURRENCY\"],\n  \"rows\": [\n    {\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"AA9901X0001\", \"VALUE_DATE\": \"2026-01-15\", \"START_DATE\": \"2026-01-15\", \"CURRENCY\": \"USD\"},\n    {\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"AA9901X0002\", \"VALUE_DATE\": \"2026-01-16\", \"START_DATE\": \"2026-01-16\", \"CURRENCY\": \"EUR\"}\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/data/import/commit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "data", "import", "commit"]
            },
            "description": "Insert rows into the target table (append mode — keeps existing data).\nRows should be the parsed CSV rows from the /import/preview step, with the column mapping applied.\n\nExpected response:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"table\": \"tstg_aa_accountdetail\",\n  \"mode\": \"append\",\n  \"rows_imported\": 2\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Import Commit — Replace",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"connection_name\": \"{{connection_name}}\",\n  \"table\": \"tstg_aa_accountdetail\",\n  \"mode\": \"replace\",\n  \"columns\": [\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", \"START_DATE\", \"CURRENCY\"],\n  \"rows\": [\n    {\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"AA9901X0001\", \"VALUE_DATE\": \"2026-01-15\", \"START_DATE\": \"2026-01-15\", \"CURRENCY\": \"USD\"},\n    {\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\": \"AA9901X0002\", \"VALUE_DATE\": \"2026-01-16\", \"START_DATE\": \"2026-01-16\", \"CURRENCY\": \"EUR\"}\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/data/import/commit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "data", "import", "commit"]
            },
            "description": "TRUNCATE the target table first, then insert rows (replace mode — wipes existing data).\nSafe to re-run multiple times without duplicate key errors.\n\nExpected response:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"table\": \"tstg_aa_accountdetail\",\n  \"mode\": \"replace\",\n  \"rows_imported\": 2\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Export",
      "description": "Export table data in various formats after generation.\n\nFormat options:\n  dml → INSERT INTO statements (engine-aware quoting)\n  csv → standard CSV\n  ddl → CREATE TABLE statement (reconstructed from live schema)\n\nAll export endpoints return plain text (not JSON) for easy copy-paste or download.\nApply filters to export a subset of the data.",
      "item": [
