            },
            "description": "Export table rows as INSERT INTO statements (plain text response).\nQuoting is engine-aware:\n  PostgreSQL  → \"schema\".\"table\"\n  Oracle      → \"SCHEMA\".\"TABLE\"\n  SQL Server  → [schema].[table]\n  MySQL       → `schema`.`table`\n\nExpected response (plain text):\n```sql\n-- DML export: tstg_aa_accountdetail  (100 rows)\n\nINSERT INTO \"banking\".\"tstg_aa_accountdetail\" (\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", ...) VALUES ('AA2406A0001', '2024-11-17', ...);\nINSERT INTO \"banking\".\"tstg_aa_accountdetail\" (\"ARRANGEMENT_ID\", \"VALUE_DATE\", ...) VALUES ('AA2408B0002', '2023-04-16', ...);\n...\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Export as DML (with filter)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
