            "description": "Export table data as CSV plain text.\n\nExpected response (plain text):\n```\nARRANGEMENT_ID,VALUE_DATE,START_DATE,DRAWDOWN_END_DATE,...\nAA2406A0001,2024-11-17,2024-11-17,2024-11-17,...\nAA2408B0002,2023-04-16,2023-04-16,2023-04-16,...\n...\n```"
          },
