            "description": "Reconstruct and return the CREATE TABLE DDL for a table (plain text).\nUseful for understanding the schema or recreating the table in another environment.\n\nExpected response (plain text):\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE \"banking\".\"tstg_aa_accountdetail\" (\n  \"ARRANGEMENT_ID\" VARCHAR NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,\n  \"VALUE_DATE\" DATE,\n  \"START_DATE\" DATE,\n  \"DRAWDOWN_END_DATE\" DATE,\n  ...\n);\n```"
